platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The next time you’re plotting an adventure, lean on the power of Tripsy to get a handle on all your trip details. Flight information, accommodations, expenses, and more are all tracked in one place, making it easy to share with your travel companions or access across devices when you’re in a pickle.
